# Comments and documentation in English

- This is an open-source library. **All source comments and documentation must be in English.**
- This includes: JSDoc, inline comments, TODO/FIXME messages, and user-facing docs (README, CHANGELOG).
- Exception: Plan/spec documents used only internally may use another language if the team agrees.
